<div class="metadata centered"><h3 class="PubTitle">A clinical research strategy using longitudinal observational data in the post-electronic health records era</h3></div>
<div class="metadata-group" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Rae Woong Park, MD<sup></sup>
</div>
<div class="metadata-group" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><p class="metadata-entry"><a id="A1"><!-- named anchor --></a>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Ajou University School of Medicine, Suwon, Korea.</p></div>
<div class="metadata centered"></div>
