<div class="metadata-group">
<div class="metadata-chunk">
<a id="idm140484454028256"><!-- named anchor --></a><p class="metadata-entry">Corresponding author: Rae Woong Park, <a href="mailto:veritas@ajou.ac.kr">veritas@ajou.ac.kr</a> </p>
</div> Received 29 June 2012       Accepted 12 July 2012<p class="metadata-entry">Copyright © 2012 Korean Medical Association </p>
